    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And I press "จองห้อง"
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Then I should be on the reserve submit for "engr303" page
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;And I should see "koonoath"

